#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:10
msgid "The MQTT HASS plugin implement MQTT Discovery for Home Assistant (HASS), including report and control of some OSPy system settings and valves (stations) over MQTT. MQTT Discovery enables automatic devices and entities enrolment from HASS user interface configuration panel, including plug-and-play availability detection, status and control."
