#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:17
msgid "An MQTT broker such as Mosquitto is required to be accessible by OSPy device and HASS. This broker can be on different parts of the local network, on a remote network, or installed on either OSPy or HASS system."
