#: plugins/mqtt_home_assistant/templates/mqtt_home_assistant_help.html:44
msgid "Topic prefix: This prefix is used for OSPy system parameters and zones published to the MQTT broker. Leave this option empty to use a slugified OSPy System name. This setting will be slugified when saved. (Default: System name or \"OSPy\" if System name is empty)."
