msgid "Cities for location"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/sunrise_and_sunset/templates/sunrise_and_sunset_help.html:66
msgid "The module includes location and time zone data for the following cities. The list includes all capital cities plus some from the UK. The list also includes the US state capitals and some other US cities."
