msgid "Wind Speed Monitor settings - help"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:8
msgid "This plugin checked wind speed, if station is switched on and actual wind speed is > wind speed value in options, switches off all selected stations in scheduler and sends E-mail with error. Preventing for fault watering while wind."
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:10
msgid "(1m/s = 3,6 km/h or 1m/s = 2,237 mile/h)."
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:11
msgid "Measurement cycle: the counter is cleared, 10 seconds are waited, from the counter read the number of pulses in 10 seconds"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:12
msgid "Formula for calculation: pulse = number of measured pulses from the counter/10. Result in m/s = (pulse/(set number of pulses per revolution * 1.0)) * set wind speed in m/s"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:13
msgid "Rounding to 2 places: result in m/s = round (result in m/s * 1.0, 2). If we want the result in km/h to 2 decimal places: result in km/h = round (result in m/s * 3.6, 2)"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:14
msgid "Current value measurement: the current wind value is measured continuously (the records in counter), but the result is processed and displayed after 10 seconds"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:15
msgid "Maximal speed measurement: if the current speed is higher than the previous maximal speed, save to log (if enabled log) is performed and the new maximal wind speed is saved"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:16
msgid "Switching off the station in case of exceeding the maximum set speed: wind in m/s maximal setup speed -> stop station"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:17
msgid "Error message at maximal wind speed: if the wind has a speed higher than 150 km/h (42 m/sec), measurement is not guaranteed an error is displayed"
msgstr ""

#: plugins/wind_monitor/templates/wind_monitor_help.html:18
msgid "Measurement accuracy very much depends on the setting of the following parameters (Number of pulses/sec, wind speed per rotation m/sec)"
msgstr ""

